creator: Real Life Church
descriptionHtml:
With the Real Life Church Ministries app, you can connect with your local or worldwide campus anywhere you take your phone.

• Watch or listen to messages from our weekend services
• Discover events and initiatives focused on growing the RLCM mission
• Invite your friends and family
• Give to your campus
• And more!

The latest version of the app has many updates to help you grow and connect easily with everything we do here at Real Life Church Ministries. Download the RLCM app today to be part of our community as we take the next step in our journey with Christ together.

About Real Life Church Ministries:
Real Life Church Ministries is a body of churches that wants to be irresistible to the unchurched. Our mission is to help people find and follow Jesus. This is done by connecting with the community through local and global outreach opportunities, along with fun and amazing community events. RLCM has physical locations in Canyon Country, CA, Simi Valley, CA and Valencia, CA. Thousands also connect with us online every week at rlcmonline.com
descriptionShort: Experience Real Life Church Ministries anywhere you take your phone.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes bug fixes and performance improvements.

We fixed an issue with the media detail page and an issue with Subsplash Live playback.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- You can send files to one another
- You can mention someone using an @ symbol to notify them directly.
- Channel managers can restrict channel invites to managers
- Managers can also set artwork and descriptions for a group channel
- Administers can set channels to be public for anyone to join

Fixed:
- Media playback now stops when you force close the app
- Fixed a Messaging issue causing link previews to cause the channel to crash

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- Direct messaging is here! Admins can enable it in the Subsplash Dashboard.
- Block other users from sending you unwanted messages.
- Share prayer requests with your group channels.
- Create polls
- Reply to past messages
- Group channels can now have up to 2,000 people.

Fixed:
- Fixed issue where typing indicator appeared in the wrong channel.
- Fixed issue causing the channel artwork to not update.
